Sure, here are some example sentences in Serbian that use the word "mila" in different forms and positions, with a star (*) next to the word:

1. *Mila* je moja najbolja prijateljica. (Mila is my best friend.)
2. Ova pesma je jako *mila* mom srcu. (This song is very dear to my heart.)
3. Ona je *mila* i ljupka kao cvet. (She is sweet and lovely like a flower.)
4. Deca su bila tako *mila* dok su spavala. (The children were so cute while they were sleeping.)
5. *Mila* sam se na njegov osmeh. (I melted at his smile.)
6. Ona mi je *mila* poput sestre. (She is dear to me like a sister.)
7. Koliko *mila* životinja! (What cute animals!)
8. Ovo je *mila* pesma koju sam ikada čula. (This is the sweetest song I've ever heard.)
9. *Mila* mi je ta tvoja haljina. (I like that dress of yours.)
10. Čini mi se da mi je ova knjiga *mila*. (It seems to me that this book is dear to me.)

I hope these examples are helpful!